@startuml seq-rf07-consultar-saldo
title RF07 - Consultar saldo diario consolidado

actor Comerciante
participant "Front Blazor" as Front
participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
participant "API Relatorios" as ApiRel
database "Redis" as Redis
database "Aurora / PostgreSQL" as DB

Comerciante -> Front: Seleciona data
Front -> APIGW: GET /api/relatorios/{dia}\nBearer JWT
APIGW -> APIGW: Valida JWT e scope\nrelatorios:read
APIGW -> ApiRel: Encaminha request

ApiRel -> Redis: GET saldo:{merchant}:{dia}
alt Cache hit - producao
    Redis --> ApiRel: Saldo consolidado
    ApiRel --> APIGW: 200 OK { dia, saldo }
    APIGW --> Front: Relatorio
    Front --> Comerciante: Exibe saldo do dia
else Cache miss
    Redis --> ApiRel: null
    ApiRel -> DB: SELECT saldos_diarios WHERE dia = :dia
    alt Registro encontrado
        DB --> ApiRel: Saldo
        ApiRel -> Redis: Repopula cache
        ApiRel --> APIGW: 200 OK { dia, saldo }
    else Sem consolidacao ainda
        DB --> ApiRel: vazio
        ApiRel --> APIGW: 204 No Content
        note right: RN07.3 - aguarda RF04/RF05
    end
    APIGW --> Front: Resposta
    Front --> Comerciante: Saldo ou estado vazio
end

@enduml
